_sText:
this is my second version i have made.

i have made a few changes

- 64 spawn points (12 ct spawn / 52 t spawn)
- 3 secrets
- 2 dynamic characters
- 3 nade spawers for the t's
- different guns for the ct's (with 1000 ammo)
- ct's cant go to the t spawn anymore


iff you find any bug or so say it and i will fix it.


i have put a lot of work in this map so pleas say what you think of it, rate the map and say what could be better.


Enjoy Mod F.E.A.R
